                     <interp inst="t18200918-249-person2343" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a cheesmonger, and live in Dorset-street, St. Marylebone. About the begining of July the prisoner brought me these papers to sell in small quantities. He said it was waste paper, which Mr. Watts had flung aside, and bid him take it away.</p>
               <p>- WATTS. I am inspector of the poor. I never gave him leave to take them. They were bound, but the bindings are now off.</p>

